column5: Hey guys  Here's a video with some clips from my 2011 season on Simcoe/Cooch.  I wish I had more footage, and with the new camera i will have lots more this upcoming season.  Thanks for watching! Cant wait for ICE!!!
Great video, Steve. Some nice chunks in there. Thanks for sharing.  ps. Get some suspenders for your shorts.
Awesome video Steve as always Loved seeing them big lakers coming out the hole  P.S.  What's that pink, redish thingy in the net?? Thanks for sharing Leechman
Lol. I was waiting for it. I've lost 60 lbs and still have most of the same wardrobe.  Thats my excuse and I'm sticking to it.  LOL.  Apparently there's this thing called a belt though
